Six people were paired up.

864
00:39:40,503 --> 00:39:42,755
-What? What if we can't go?
-What were we doing?

865
00:39:42,838 --> 00:39:46,300
I was excited after holding his hand,

866
00:39:46,384 --> 00:39:47,927
