867
00:39:48,010 --> 00:39:50,179
<i>It was like they snatched it away from us.</i>

868
00:39:51,389 --> 00:39:54,183
<i>If you want to go on a date,</i>

869
00:39:54,266 --> 00:39:57,061
<i>you must now try to win the king's favor.</i>

870
00:40:00,272 --> 00:40:01,440
-For real?
-What is this?

871
00:40:01,524 --> 00:40:02,525
Are they being serious?

872
00:40:03,567 --> 00:40:04,985
That's a pretty powerful privilege.

873
00:40:05,069 --> 00:40:06,529
-Seriously.
-It's awesome.

874
00:40:06,612 --> 00:40:08,280
We have to stay in his good grace.

875
00:40:08,364 --> 00:40:10,449
Because of this king,

876
00:40:10,533 --> 00:40:12,660
