877
00:40:12,743 --> 00:40:14,203
I wanted to be king too.

878
00:40:15,746 --> 00:40:17,456
He can match the date partners?

879
00:40:17,540 --> 00:40:19,708
-He's interested in Ga-yeon, right?
-Yeah.

880
00:40:19,792 --> 00:40:22,920
He's going to try to break up
Ga-yeon and Jung-min.

881
00:40:23,003 --> 00:40:24,171
-He won't let them go.
-Yeah.

882
00:40:24,255 --> 00:40:26,090
So if the feelings are mutual,

883
00:40:26,173 --> 00:40:27,967
they can put a lot in
and make the other person king.

884
00:40:28,050 --> 00:40:29,009
-Right.
-If not,

885
00:40:29,093 --> 00:40:31,470
they can put less in to prevent
someone else from becoming king.

886
00:40:31,554 --> 00:40:33,722
There's going to be a huge mind game.

887
00:40:33,806 --> 00:40:35,724
So I have the power to change your dates.

888
00:40:35,808 --> 00:40:38,227
You can pick the person
and match them with someone.

889
00:40:38,310 --> 00:40:39,353
The four includes you.

890
00:40:39,437 --> 00:40:41,063
-I suppose so.
-We have to curry his favor.

891
00:40:41,147 --> 00:40:42,815
Exclude yourself
and let four people go on dates.

892
00:40:42,898 --> 00:40:44,608
-Yeah.
-Right.

893
00:40:44,692 --> 00:40:46,444
You're so cocky.

894
00:40:51,198 --> 00:40:52,324
You're right, my king.

895
00:40:53,451 --> 00:40:55,494
<i>Nothing good can come</i>
<i>from being on his bad side.</i>

896
00:40:56,495 --> 00:40:57,913
<i>The king's power is immense.</i>

897
00:40:57,997 --> 00:40:59,498
He may become a tyrant.

898
00:40:59,582 --> 00:41:00,583
I know. I'm scared.

899
00:41:01,167 --> 00:41:03,502
<i>Becoming king really went to his head</i>

900
00:41:03,586 --> 00:41:05,337
that I kind of couldn't stand him.

901
00:41:07,047 --> 00:41:08,340
Would you like something to eat?

902
00:41:08,424 --> 00:41:09,675
I'm okay.

903
00:41:09,758 --> 00:41:11,635
-You're doing a good job.
-No.

904
00:41:11,719 --> 00:41:13,345
<i>I had no choice.</i>

905
00:41:13,429 --> 00:41:15,014
But I hated this reality.

906
00:41:15,097 --> 00:41:16,599
-I should learn from her.
-I know.

907
00:41:16,682 --> 00:41:19,894
<i>When I saw Chae-rin</i>
<i>trying to win the king's favor,</i>

908
00:41:19,977 --> 00:41:22,480
it secretly made me feel good.

909
00:41:22,563 --> 00:41:24,607
I felt like we were on the same team.

910
00:41:24,690 --> 00:41:25,941
What do you want for breakfast?

911
00:41:26,025 --> 00:41:27,818
First of all,

912
00:41:27,902 --> 00:41:29,361
I'd like my steak to be medium-rare.

913
00:41:29,945 --> 00:41:31,113
I can

914
00:41:31,197 --> 00:41:33,949
serve primarily Korean dishes for you.

915
00:41:34,033 --> 00:41:34,950
Serve?

916
00:41:35,910 --> 00:41:37,369
WORKING HER ANGLE

917
00:41:38,454 --> 00:41:42,541
Since the king can match people up,
Hye-won can go on a date too.

918
00:41:42,625 --> 00:41:46,795
I'll serve you very healthy
and delicious Korean dishes.

919
00:41:46,879 --> 00:41:49,423
Okay. Got it.

920
00:41:49,507 --> 00:41:50,966
You're going though, right?

921
00:41:51,050 --> 00:41:52,676
Me? Of course.

922
00:41:53,802 --> 00:41:56,305
Kyung-ho may seem very arrogant, right?

923
00:41:56,388 --> 00:41:58,349
But the really arrogant one is Ye-rim.

924
00:41:58,432 --> 00:41:59,391
She is

925
00:41:59,475 --> 00:42:01,352
-acting like the queen.
-Ye-rim thinks

926
00:42:01,435 --> 00:42:03,020
she's definitely going out.

927
00:42:06,273 --> 00:42:08,526
-"You're going though, right?"
-"I don't have to do that."

928
00:42:08,609 --> 00:42:09,652
"You're going though, right?"

929
00:42:10,236 --> 00:42:11,654
What a burden.

930
00:42:13,572 --> 00:42:15,407
GO TO THE HEART ROOM
AND DECIDE THE DATES FOR TOMORROW

931
00:42:15,491 --> 00:42:16,659
-What did it say?
-What?

932
00:42:16,742 --> 00:42:19,703
Only His Majesty seems to
have gotten the text.

933
00:42:21,372 --> 00:42:22,289
I'll be back.

934
00:42:24,833 --> 00:42:26,168
He's on his way to decide.

935
00:42:26,252 --> 00:42:27,419
I'm so curious.

936
00:42:27,503 --> 00:42:28,963
I want to get a text too.

937
00:42:29,046 --> 00:42:32,091
The king can change
the partner of your date too, right?

938
00:42:32,174 --> 00:42:33,259
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

939
00:42:33,342 --> 00:42:34,385
The way he wants.

940
00:42:34,468 --> 00:42:35,886
I should've flattered him more.

941
00:42:36,387 --> 00:42:37,429
I should've been faster.

942
00:42:45,771 --> 00:42:46,897
HEART ROOM

943
00:42:48,857 --> 00:42:51,694
<i>The voting booth</i>
<i>in the Heart Room has closed,</i>

944
00:42:51,777 --> 00:42:54,280
<i>and the king’s office has now opened.</i>

945
00:43:01,954 --> 00:43:04,039
<i>The first king Kang Kyung-ho must</i>

946
00:43:04,123 --> 00:43:06,166
<i>think about each participant one by one</i>

947
00:43:06,250 --> 00:43:08,502
<i>and match them up on dates</i>
<i>however you want.</i>

948
00:43:08,586 --> 00:43:10,879
<i>Within four people,</i>
<i>the number of dates and combinations</i>

949
00:43:10,963 --> 00:43:12,172
<i>are completely up to you.</i>

950
00:43:12,256 --> 00:43:15,092
EXAMPLE: 1 KING AND 3 WOMEN
OR 1 KING AND 1 WOMAN, 1 MAN AND 1 WOMAN

951
00:43:15,175 --> 00:43:17,595
-"One king and three women."
-He can go out with two women?

952
00:43:18,178 --> 00:43:19,513
No way. Don't you dare.

953
00:43:19,597 --> 00:43:22,182
Why do I get the feeling that
he'll choose three women?

954
00:43:38,866 --> 00:43:43,162
THE KING IS IN DEEP ANGUISH

955
00:43:48,292 --> 00:43:50,419
KING

956
00:43:55,215 --> 00:43:56,050
YE-RIM

957
00:43:56,133 --> 00:43:59,136
<i>First, I'll go on a date with Ye-rim.</i>

958
00:43:59,219 --> 00:44:01,639
THE KING PONDERS OVER THE NEXT DECISION

959
00:44:04,767 --> 00:44:07,561
<i>I used my brain a bit.</i>

960
00:44:09,688 --> 00:44:11,273
<i>I'll go on a date twice.</i>

961
00:44:11,357 --> 00:44:12,191
KANG KYUNG-HO

962
00:44:12,274 --> 00:44:13,108
PARK JUNG-MIN

963
00:44:13,192 --> 00:44:14,360
PARK DO-GEON

964
00:44:18,656 --> 00:44:21,950
<i>Ga-yeon can go on a date with Jung-min.</i>

965
00:44:22,951 --> 00:44:26,288
Me and Ye-rim, Ga-yeon and me,

966
00:44:26,372 --> 00:44:28,123
and Ga-yeon and Jung-min.

967
00:44:28,207 --> 00:44:29,041
4 PEOPLE IN TOTAL

968
00:44:29,124 --> 00:44:30,417
Let me beat him.

969
00:44:30,501 --> 00:44:32,670
I like head-on showdowns.

970
00:44:35,631 --> 00:44:38,634
WHAT IS THE KING'S FINAL DECISION?

971
00:44:39,343 --> 00:44:42,346
The more we talk about this,
I want to become a king more.

972
00:44:42,429 --> 00:44:44,056
-I know.
-It must be so fun.

973
00:44:44,139 --> 00:44:45,766
-I hope you become king.
-Yeah.

974
00:44:45,849 --> 00:44:47,476
I need your help.

975
00:44:47,559 --> 00:44:49,103
Should we join forces to help him?

976
00:44:49,853 --> 00:44:51,438
Should we join forces to help him?

977
00:44:51,522 --> 00:44:53,315
We'll plot together.

978
00:44:53,399 --> 00:44:54,900
Wait, if the men act too cocky,

979
00:44:54,983 --> 00:44:56,610
